ne":55,"column":28,"offset":4149},"indent":[]},"value":"zettel.20260421171637"}],"anchors":{"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka":{"type":"header","text":"Pertanyaan yang dibuka","value":"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"klaim-utama":{"type":"header","text":"Klaim utama","value":"klaim-utama","line":21,"column":0,"depth":2},"peran-bmad-product-brief":{"type":"header","text":"Peran BMAD Product Brief","value":"peran-bmad-product-brief","line":27,"column":0,"depth":2},"kapan-direkomendasikan":{"type":"header","text":"Kapan direkomendasikan?","value":"kapan-direkomendasikan","line":38,"column":0,"depth":2},"output-yang-berguna":{"type":"header","text":"Output yang berguna","value":"output-yang-berguna","line":42,"column":0,"depth":2},"lihat-juga":{"type":"header","text":"Lihat juga","value":"lihat-juga","line":53,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":[],"parent":"zettel","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"bmad-product-brief-merapikan-visi-produk-sebelum-prd\">BMAD product brief merapikan visi produk sebelum PRD<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bmad-product-brief-merapikan-visi-produk-sebelum-prd\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\">Pertanyaan yang dibuka<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pertanyaan-yang-dibuka\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Apa tujuan BMAD Product Brief?</li>\n<li>Kapan Anda memakai Product Brief, bukan PRFAQ?</li>\n<li>Apa bedanya Product Brief dengan PRD?</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"klaim-utama\">Klaim utama<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#klaim-utama\"></a></h2>\n<p>BMAD Product Brief bukan pra-PRD untuk semua situasi. Ia adalah jalur yang lebih lembut ketika ide sudah cukup jelas, tetapi masih perlu diringkas dan dijelaskan secara strategis.</p>\n<p>Product Brief berfungsi untuk mentransisi visi yang sudah ada menjadi bentuk yang bisa diberi makan ke PRD berikutnya.</p>\n<h2 id=\"peran-bmad-product-brief\">Peran BMAD Product Brief<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#peran-bmad-product-brief\"></a></h2>\n<p>Dalam BMAD, brief membantu Anda:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>merangkum target customer dan masalah utama,</li>\n<li>menegaskan nilai proposisi awal,</li>\n<li>membatasi ruang lingkup tanpa memaksa pendekatan teknis,</li>\n<li>menjelaskan keyakinan strategi secara ringkas.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ini berbeda dari PRD karena Product Brief tidak bertujuan mengunci semua kebutuhan. Ia bertujuan memberi arah yang lebih jelas sebelum requirement formal dibentuk.</p>\n<h2 id=\"kapan-direkomendasikan\">Kapan direkomendasikan?<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#kapan-direkomendasikan\"></a></h2>\n<p>Produk yang Anda selami sudah memiliki arah tetapi masih memerlukan penyusunan. Ideal untuk kasus di mana Anda tidak butuh penekanan kritis PRFAQ, tetapi butuh klarifikasi sebelum Planning.</p>\n<h2 id=\"output-yang-berguna\">Output yang berguna<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#output-yang-berguna\"></a></h2>\n<p>Setelah membuat Product Brief, Anda harus memiliki:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>narasi produk yang jelas,</li>\n<li>target audien yang terdefinisi,</li>\n<li>masalah utama dan nilai utama,</li>\n<li>batasan scope awal.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Itu membuat Planning lebih cepat dan mengurangi asumsi kabur masuk ke PRD.</p>\n<h2 id=\"lihat-juga\">Lihat juga<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#lihat-juga\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171633\">BMAD brainstorming memperjelas ide sebelum requirement</a> — BMAD brainstorming memperjelas ide sebelum requirement</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171638\">BMAD PRFAQ menguji ide dengan pendekatan adversarial sebelum planning</a> — BMAD PRFAQ menguji ide dengan pendekatan adversarial sebelum planning</li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171457\">BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</a> — BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"tags\">Tags<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#tags\"></a></h2>\n<ol>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">bmad (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">analysis-phase (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">product-brief (Private)</a></li>\n<li><a title=\"Private\" href=\"https://wiki.dendron.so/notes/hfyvYGJZQiUwQaaxQO27q.html\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"private\">ai-native (Private)</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel\">Zettelkasten</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171457\">BMAD analysis phase menghentikan ketidakjelasan sebelum berubah jadi PRD dan architecture</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171638\">BMAD PRFAQ menguji ide dengan pendekatan adversarial sebelum planning</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171824\">BMAD Product Brief vs PRFAQ: klarifikasi lembut versus pengujian adversarial</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.20260421171825\">Simulasi BMAD analysis phase: invoice app untuk freelancer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.ai-native\">MOC AI-native engineering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/sotoy/notes/zettel.moc.software-architecture\">MOC: Software Architecture</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"root","title":"Hello and Welcome! 👋","desc":"","updated":1742030256619,"created":1646842475821,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"453f88f4a5f1ad7629ebb7cc49502125","links":[],"anchors":{"find-more":{"type":"header","text":"Find More","value":"find-more","line":20,"column":0,"depth":2}},"children":["book-summaries","daily","handbook","notes","tags","til","zettel"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"\nWelcome to the homepage! I use Dendron to store and organize notes, ideas, and experiments I’m working on. Here are the main sections you’ll find on this site:\n\n1. **Learning Notes** — Practical notes on programming, recent technologies, and productivity tips.\n2. **Personal Projects** — Summaries of projects, experiments, and outcomes I’m working on or have completed.\n3. **Writings & Opinions** — Casual articles and reflections about technology, daily life, and other interesting topics.\n\nI’m constantly experimenting and learning. I hope the content here helps you as a reference, a starting point for discussion, or just light reading.\n\n> Why Dendron?\n>\nDendron helps keep notes organized. Its \"seed\" and \"vault\" concepts make it easy to structure content and find what you need.\n\n## Find More\n\nIf you want to learn more or connect, check these links:\n\n- [Homepage (Dendron)](https://zeihanaulia.github.io/sotoy/)\n- [My GitHub](https://github.com/zeihanaulia)\n- [My Twitter / X](https://x.com/zeihanaulia)\n\nThanks for stopping by. If you have feedback or want to chat, feel free to reach out.\n"},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"dendronVersion":"0.83.0","vaults":[{"fsPath":"vault"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat"